<section class="hero">

<h1>
Precision <span>Medicine</span>
</h1>

<p>
Precision medicine microbiomics studies how microbial communities influence individual disease risk, therapeutic response, immune regulation, nutrition, drug metabolism, and personalized health strategies.
</p>

<div class="hero-image">
  <img
